---
const faqs = [
  {
    q: 'Who can join?',
    a: 'Top-tier retail & e-commerce leaders and early-stage technology companies (typically 10–50 people) working on relevant solutions.',
  },
  {
    q: 'What is the format of the meetings?',
    a: 'One Expert Merchant (eg. a CMO, CDO, Head of Ecommerce) and between 2–4 tech leaders and entrepreneurs each have the opportunity to present what they do and receive feedback and insights about the market and potential opportunities.',
  },
  {
    q: 'How long is the call?',
    a: 'Conversations are usually capped at 1 hour.',
  },
  {
    q: 'Is there a cost to participate?',
    a: 'The Innovation Circle works on a meeting credits system. 1 Credit costs €50. Each meeting will cost a certain number of credits (maximum 4), depending on who the meeting is with. E.g. a middle-market brand = 2 credits (€100), Tier 1 = 3 credits (€150), VIP = 4 credits (€200).',
  },
];
---

<section id="faq" class="border-b border-hairline">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 py-24 md:py-32">
    <div class="text-center">
      <p class="mb-5 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-fog">FAQ</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight md:text-4xl">Good to know</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 border-y border-hairline">
      {
        faqs.map((f) => (
          <details class="group border-b border-hairline last:border-b-0">
            <summary class="flex cursor-pointer list-none items-center justify-between gap-4 py-6 text-lg font-medium [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden">
              {f.q}
              <span class="flex-none text-2xl font-light text-fog transition-transform duration-200 group-open:rotate-45">
                +
              </span>
            </summary>
            <p class="pb-6 leading-relaxed text-mist/70">{f.a}</p>
          </details>
        ))
      }
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
